{"id":3911,"date":"2025-06-06T11:16:27","date_gmt":"2025-06-06T04:16:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3911"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:17:01","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:17:01","slug":"cac-loai-mun-o-mat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/cac-loai-mun-o-mat\/","title":{"rendered":"5 lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia GSC"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o? M\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u phi\u1ec1n to\u00e1i trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb. T\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c nhau. Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fang m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-hinh-thanh-nhu-the-nao-nhung-yeu-to-gay-mun-pho-bien\"><\/span><b>M\u1ee5n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211; M\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 (Acne) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da li\u1ec5u ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t, c\u1ed5, l\u01b0ng, vai,\u2026 \u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t s\u1ea7n, s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee9a nh\u00e2n m\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3912\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3912\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3912\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-1.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3912\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c nhau, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn: N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh, l\u00e0m l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eebng h\u00f3a l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng: Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft di\u1ec5n ra b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. Khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 vi khu\u1ea9n: Khi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng da m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Vi khu\u1ea9n P. acnes c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh, k\u00edch th\u00edch vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam: C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-loai-cac-dang-mun-khong-viem\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111au, s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hay nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. Ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-an\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u1ea8n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o b\u1ecf qua M\u1ee5n \u1ea9n. L\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1edbp da, c\u00f3 ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, k\u00e9m m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3913\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3913\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3913\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-2.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n \u1ea8n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3913\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n \u1ea8n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Kh\u00f4ng s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn da th\u00f4 r\u00e1p<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u00e1n, c\u1eb1m, quai h\u00e0m<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Kh\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y trang, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng k\u1ef9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u silicon, g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 ng\u1ecdt, cay n\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-dau-trang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh khi l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc b\u1edfi d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n nh\u1ecf, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee5c, n\u1eb1m b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3914\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3914\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3914\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-3.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3914\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 1 \u2013 2mm<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111au, kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u0169i, tr\u00e1n, c\u1eb1m v\u00e0 hai b\u00ean m\u00e1<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec, mang thai<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t ch\u01b0a khoa h\u1ecdc, th\u1ee9c khuya, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-dau-den\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0110\u1ea7u \u0110en<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, b\u1ecb oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u00e0u n\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c \u0111en.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3915\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3915\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3915\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-4.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n \u0110\u1ea7u \u0110en\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3915\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n \u0110\u1ea7u \u0110en<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n nh\u1ecf, s\u1eabm m\u00e0u, nh\u00f4 nh\u1eb9 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Kh\u00f4ng s\u01b0ng, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111au<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T (m\u0169i, tr\u00e1n, c\u1eb1m), c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 vai<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc do b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u0103m s\u00f3c sai c\u00e1ch, nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-biet-cac-dang-mun-viem-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-boc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211;\u00a0 <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee7 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f4i khi k\u00e8m theo m\u00e1u. M\u1ee5n g\u00e2y s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111au nh\u1ee9c v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m ho\u1eb7c s\u1eb9o l\u1ed3i tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng do d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3917\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3917\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3917\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-5.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3917\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-nhot\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n nh\u1ecdt<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211; M\u1ee5n nh\u1ecdt l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m da, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng n\u1ed1t s\u01b0ng ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7, g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c. Lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u1eb7t, c\u1eb1m, l\u01b0ng ho\u1eb7c v\u00f9ng da c\u00f3 tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n nh\u1ecdt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi khu\u1ea9n x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o nang l\u00f4ng, g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00e0y s\u1eebng nang l\u00f4ng, khi\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng khoa h\u1ecdc: \u0103n u\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t, ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-nang\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n nang<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n nang l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t s\u01b0ng to, ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee7, g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. Khi v\u1ee1, m\u1ee5n nang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m lan vi khu\u1ea9n sang v\u00f9ng da kh\u00e1c, g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n nang:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn do d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec ho\u1eb7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a corticoid, g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3918\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3918\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3918\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-6.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n nang\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3918\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n nang<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-loai-mun-o-mat-%e2%80%93-mun-dinh-rau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211; <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111inh r\u00e2u<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111inh r\u00e2u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng n\u1eb7ng. Khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o, m\u1ee5n th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3ng, \u0111au, \u0111\u00f4i khi g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng m\u00e1u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy c\u01a1 t\u1eafc m\u1ea1ch, g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea7n tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-loai-mun-o-mat-%e2%80%93-mun-viem-do\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211;\u00a0 <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn do vi khu\u1ea9n P. acnes g\u00e2y ra. M\u1ee5n c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf, s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam, \u0111\u00f4i khi ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7, g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m da k\u00e9m m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, tinh b\u1ed9t, thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ho\u1eb7c v\u1ec7 sinh da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-dang-mun-khac-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam. Th\u00ec l\u00e0n da c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-loai-mun-o-mat-%e2%80%93-mun-coc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211; M\u1ee5n c\u00f3c<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n c\u00f3c do virus HPV g\u00e2y ra, th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ch\u1eadm trong kho\u1ea3ng 6 &#8211; 12 th\u00e1ng. M\u1ee5n khi\u1ebfn v\u00f9ng da xung quanh tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e2y lan.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-loai-mun-o-mat-%e2%80%93-mun-hat-ke\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t &#8211; <\/span><\/i><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n h\u1ea1t k\u00ea<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n th\u1ecbt l\u00e0 c\u00e1c u nang nh\u1ecf ch\u1ee9a keratin, th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1m tr\u00ean da. Lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan r\u1ed9ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-quen-giup-ngan-ngua-mun-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><b>Th\u00f3i quen gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khoa h\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3919\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3919\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3919\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-7.webp\" alt=\"Th\u00f3i quen gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-7.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-7-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-7-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/33-7-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3919\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Th\u00f3i quen gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng retinol \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft 2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, ng\u0103n m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean m\u1eb7t, tr\u00e1nh l\u00e2y lan vi khu\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc 10h t\u1ed1i, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m tinh b\u1ed9t, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da ngay sau khi \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Peel da \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 <strong>c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t<\/strong>, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u1eefu \u00edch. H\u00e3y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo d\u00f5i website c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p soi c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n \u1edf m\u1eb7t g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o? Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fang m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3920,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3911","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3911","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3911"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3911\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3968,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3911\/revisions\/3968"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3920"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3911"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3911"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3911"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}